38317>>>>>                // If from child, this is a probably a parent Zoom from a Zoom.
38317>>>>>                Case Break
38318>>>>>
38318>>>>>            Case Else // must be nfUndefined
38318>>>>>
38318>>>>>        Case End
38318>>>>>
38318>>>>>        Send SetActionButtons
